('THIQUE', 'Em THIQUE, Beyoncé celebra o corpo feminino, a sensualidade e o desejo sexual de forma explícita e poderosa. A música subverte a ideia de que a magreza é o único padrão de beleza, exaltando a beleza e a atitude de um corpo “thique” (encorpado, cheio de curvas). A faixa também tem uma conotação financeira, usando a palavra “thique” para se referir à prosperidade. O ritmo traz uma sensação de urgência e afirmação.', 2, 5, '4:04', 'That''s that thique (T) That''s that thique (H) That''s that thique (I) That''s that thique (Q) That''s that thique (U) That''s that thique (E) That''s that thique (T) That''s that thique (H) That''s that thique (I) That''s that thique (Q) That''s that thique (U) That''s that thique (E) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) The kind of body, make a nigga wanna crawl (ayy) Got him on his knees, he already on the floor (ayy) Got a body full of money and a tank on E (ayy) But I''m out here lookin'' for somethin'' to eat (ayy) Thick like a stallion, can''t control it, I''m wildin'' He said he want it, I buy it, I''m livin'' life in abundance I don''t know how to stop, I ain''t never gon'' drop I be doin'' the most, I ain''t never gon'' flop They be lookin'' at me, I be lookin'' at them I be smokin'' on him, I be drivin'' a Benz Got that body, it''s gon'' cost a billion Got that body, it''s gon'' cost a trillion That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) That''s that thique, that''s that thique (that''s that) The kind of body, make a nigga wanna crawl (ayy) Got him on his knees, he already on the floor (ayy) Got a body full of money and a tank on E (ayy) But I''m out here lookin'' for somethin'' to eat (ayy) Thick like a stallion