('PURE/HONEY', 'PURE/HONEY é uma faixa dividida em duas partes, que se fundem em um hino definitivo para a cultura ballroom. A primeira parte, PURE, celebra a autenticidade e a beleza natural (Pure), enquanto a segunda, HONEY, é uma homenagem às lendas do voguing e à comunidade LGBTQIA+. As letras são cheias de códigos, referenciando as batalhas de passarela (walking in the face, walking in the drag), a confiança inabalável (The only thing plastic is the seat on the toilet) e o orgulho de quem define as próprias regras.', 2, 5, '4:48', 'You got it (pure) Honey (honey) You got it (pure) Honey (honey) (Honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) You got it I can''t imagine (I can''t imagine) Look at my body (look at my body) I am the fashion (I am the fashion) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) I can''t imagine (I can''t imagine) Look at my body (look at my body) I am the fashion (I am the fashion) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) Honey (honey, honey, honey) It''s the confidence and the look, the walk, the face (pure) I love myself and I ain''t afraid to show it, show it, show it (pure) Confidence, confidence, honey (pure) This ain''t a fantasy, this is all for real (pure) It''s all up in my mind, it''s all up in my feelings (pure) Got that body, got that booty, don''t need no filler (pure) I''m so clean, so fresh, so pure, so real (pure) I''m a real girl, I''m a real girl (pure) Don''t need no man, I''m in my feelings (pure) I''m so fine, I''m so cold (pure) Confidence, confidence, honey (pure) The only thing plastic is the seat on the toilet (pure) Pure, pure, pure (pure) It''s a feeling, I can''t help it, I''m not afraid to show it (pure) Walk in the room, I''m takin'' all the light, that''s right (pure) I ain''t afraid to show it, I ain''t afraid to show it (pure) Walk in the room, I''m takin'' all the lig