('Mark My Words', 'Em Mark My Words, Justin Bieber reforça, por meio da repetição da frase-título, seu compromisso de mudança e reconquista no relacionamento com Selena Gomez. A música expressa seu desejo de recuperar a confiança perdida, mostrando que suas intenções vão além de palavras, com disposição real para provar seu amor.', 4, 11, '2:14', 'Mark my words That''s all that I have Mark my words Give you all I got In every way, I will You''re the only reason why Oh, I don''t wanna live a lie Mark my words Mark my words So you heard it all before? Falling in and out of trust Trying to rekindle us Only to lose yourself But I won''t let me lose you And I won''t let us just fade away After all that we''ve been through I''ma show you more than I ever could say Mark my words That''s all that I have Mark my words Give you all I got In every way, I will You''re the only reason why Oh, I don''t wanna live a lie Mark my words Mark my words'),
('Ill Show You', 'Em I''ll Show You, Justin Bieber revela sua vulnerabilidade, lembrando que é humano e sente pressões como qualquer pessoa. O videoclipe na Islândia reforça sua busca por autenticidade e paz interior, mostrando-o afastado da exposição pública.', 4, 11, '3:19', 'My life is a movie And everyone’s watching So let’s get to the good part And passed all the non-sense Sometimes it’s hard to do the right thing When the pressure is coming down like lightening It’s like they want me to be perfect When they don’t even know that I’m hurting ''Cause life’s not easy I’m not made out of steel Don’t forget that I’m human Don’t forget that I’m real Act like you know me But you never will But there’s one thing that I know for sure I’ll show you I’ll show you I’ll show you I’ve got to learn things Learn them the hard way Got to see what it feels like No matter what they say Sometimes it’s hard to do the right thing When the pressure is coming down like lightening It’s like they want me to be perfect When they don’t even know that I’m hurting ''Cause life’s not easy I’m not made out of steel Don’t forget that I’m human Don’t forget that I’m real Act like you know me But you never will But there’s one thing that I know for sure I’ll show you I’ll show you I’ll show you ''Cause life’s not easy I’m not made out of steel Don’t forget that I’m human Don’t forget that I’m real Act like you know me But you never will But there’s one thing that I know for sure I’ll show you I’ll show you'),
('What Do You Mean?', 'Em What Do You Mean?, Justin Bieber aborda a frustração de lidar com sinais contraditórios em relacionamentos, mostrando como palavras e gestos podem transmitir intenções opostas, inspirando-se em suas próprias experiências amorosas.', 4, 11, '3:25', 'What do you mean? Oh, oh When you nod your head yes, but you wanna say no What do you mean? Hey, yeah When you don''t want me to move, but you tell me to go What do you mean? Oh, what do you mean? Said you''re running outta time, what do you mean? Oh, oh, oh, what do you mean? Better make up your mind, what do you mean? You’re so indecisive of what I’m saying Tryna catch the beat, make up your heart Don''t know if you''re happy or complaining Don''t want for us to end, where do I start? First you wanna go to the left, then you wanna turn right Wanna argue all day, make love all night First you''re up, then you’re down and then between Oh, I really wanna know What do you mean? Oh, oh When you nod your head yes, but you wanna say no What do you mean? Hey, yeah When you don''t want me to move, but you tell me to go What do you mean? Oh, what do you mean? Said you''re running outta time, what do you mean? Oh, oh, oh, what do you mean? Better make up your mind, what do you mean? You’re overprotective when I’m leaving Tryna compromise but I can’t win You wanna make a point, but you keep preaching You had me from the start, won''t let this end First you wanna go to the left, then you wanna turn right Wanna argue all day, make love all night First you''re up, then you’re down and then between Oh, I really wanna know What do you mean? Oh, oh When you nod your head yes, but you wanna say no What do you mean? Hey, yeah When you don''t want me to move, but you tell me to go What do you mean? (I wanna know) Oh, what do you mean? (Ooh) Said you''re running outta time, what do you mean? (Oh, baby) Oh, oh, oh, what do you mean? Better make up your mind, what do you mean? Oh, oh (don''t be so selfish, baby, yeah)