('Missing You', 'A música fala sobre um relacionamento que já se desgastou completamente. O eu lírico está cansado das brigas, dos jogos emocionais e da falta de clareza da outra pessoa. Ele percebe que, mesmo que ela vá embora, ele não tem mais energia ou vontade de impedir o sentimento esfriou. A repetição mostrando que ele não vai sentir falta nem amar mais reforça que a relação chegou ao fim emocional antes do fim real. É uma música sobre desilusão, exaustão e desapego inevitável.', 9, 25, '3:05', 'Have you fucked up from the last time? You think you got everyone figured out We are leavin'' in a glass house Cause everything is shadowing all around Now tell me what you mad about I''m tired of developing nonsense And if you were to leave me now I probably do nothing to stop it I won''t be missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Touch you little more! Not love you anymore! Is that what you really want? Is that what you really want? Have you fucked up from the last time? You think you got everyone figured out We are leavin'' in a glass house Cause everything is shadowing all around Now tell me what you mad about I''m tired of developing nonsense And if you were to leave me now I probably do nothing to stop it Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Touch you little more! Not love you anymore! Is that what you really want? Is that what you really want? Now you can go spin your game girl Go-go-go on with your game girl Now you can go spin your game girl Go-go-go on with your game girl Have you fucked up from the last time? You think you got everyone figured out We are leavin'' in a glass house Cause everything is shadowing all around Now tell me what you mad about I''m tired of developing nonsense And if you were to leave me now I probably do nothing to stop it Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Missing you anymore! Touch you little more! Not love you anymore! Is that what you really want? Is that what you really want?'),
('Choose', 'A música apresenta uma narradora que se recusa a aceitar menos do que merece e exige atitudes concretas antes de se envolver com alguém. Ela deixa claro que não é facilmente impressionada e não vai dizer sim sem que a outra pessoa prove seu valor. Ao repetir You wanna make me choose, a música enfatiza que a decisão depende de demonstrações reais de compromisso, e não de promessas vazias. É uma afirmação de autovalorização, limites claros e independência emocional.', 9, 25, '3:57', 'Ahhh yeah! Ah, ah yeah Choose, you wanna make me choose You got to show me something now Why should I be with you?! You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose Not easily impressed, no! Not settling for less, no! You want me to say yes, oh well! You better bring your best hope (no)! Help me make up my mind, ah! Prove that you''re worth my time Give me a reason why it should be With you tonightbaby Make me believe it''s all you No matter what they all do Don''t want to play no games I won''t tease you and it won''t stall you But don''t you think it''s all you? If you want sex than it''s all you! And no I don''t want your number And no I don''t want to call you You want to make me choose You got to show me something now Why I should be with you?! You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose Make me believe it''s all you No matter what they all do Don''t want to play no games I won''t tease you and it won''t stall you But don''t you think it''s all you? If you want sex than it''s all you! And no I don''t want your number And no I don''t want to call you Choose you wanna make me choose You got to show me something now Why should I be with you?! Choose you wanna make me choose You got to show me something now Why should I be with you?! You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose You wanna make me choose'),
('How Soon Is Now', 'A música fala sobre alguém que se recusa a aceitar menos do que merece em um relacionamento. A pessoa exige provas reais de interesse, compromisso e valor, deixando claro que não vai cair em joguinhos, não está impressionada facilmente e não vai escolher alguém que não mostre esforço verdadeiro. A mensagem central é: se você quer ficar comigo, prove por que vale a pena.', 9, 25, '4:10', 'After tonight, there''ll be no coming home soon No tears of regret, no smell of her perfume No more dancing feet, to the beats that go boom While I watch the sunrise all alone in my room Tonight there''ll be no pouring rain No eyes wide shut to your never ending game After tonight there''ll be no me and you No distant memories past for me to hold on to See everybody''s working to hold on to what they know So I guess I kept belive in my tonight will never go Some spend a lifetime searchin trying to figure out When hell stops and heaven begins How soon is now?'),
